AUDIO: '&lt;b&gt;Cloud Code has been getting a lot of&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;attention lately, but it\'s not the only&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;AI coding tool worth using.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;Open Code is growing in popularity and&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;for good reason. It\'s 100% open source,&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;it supports multiple&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;providers and models, including free&lt;/b&gt;'

